The paper proposes a machine learning approach to solve optimal control problems, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of several subfields in computer science. The use of mixture of experts (MoE) model suggests that the paper is likely to be related to machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The numerical examples involve benchmark problems in robotics (cs.RO), and the use of neural networks as a comparison suggests that the paper may also be related to neural networks (cs.NE).
